{"tid":1030712,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求教師轉行建議","createTime":"2019-02-21T06:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T11:03:10.000Z","uid":238236,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce56a7455a601b2886dbb4c3e71833507d1db51","tid":1030712,"uid":238236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，我13年係三大社科畢業。眾所周知，社科係無專業資格的學科，由於唔知做乜好，同好有熱誠去改變社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以報左full time 通識pgde，佢又收我。<br />\n<br />\n一年之後（2014），去左間中學做Assistant Teacher，第二年(2015)去到另一間做合約老師，以為之後好好景。<br />\n<br />\n點知去到學期尾佢地話唔夠錢續約。嗰年好灰機，於是去左間出版社做編輯，發覺唔係好啱自己性格，因為環境太寧靜，無乜機會同人溝通。<br />\n<br />\n所以2017/18年學期死死地氣揾左間學校做TA至今，但學校暗示下年唔會Keep我個位。眼見身邊的人事業都起飛，自己就停滯不前。年年揾學校我唔介意，但我介意自己事業毫無成長，甚至係倒退。<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有冇人可以點條路我行適合做咩？<br />\n<br />\n除左教書，好似無乜技能。真係好煩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e2fb046abefda3c9db18a255df8c502ebcf110","tid":1030712,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"AT 同 TA 分別幾錢人工？<br />\n做補習天皇囉如果係靚仔靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b011ddd721f5dcd369b33275f9e081ff85af7e","tid":1030712,"uid":238236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1e2fb046abefda3c9db18a255df8c502ebcf110","tid":1030712,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"AT 同 TA 分別幾錢人工？<br />\n做補習天皇囉如果係靚仔靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"都係13.5k"},{"pid":"67075693edfae47406986cb1d641d62ada01c4c4","tid":1030712,"uid":148192,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:50:39.000Z","msg":"Breaking bad"},{"pid":"9d1ea18b8bd3f348a7a6aa35c80ad5e8316c3c66","tid":1030712,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"出版社編輯我估20K不過"},{"pid":"71eccd6